::: {.callout-important icon=false appearance="minimal"}

As presented in @tbl-wb1-wb2-comp-results, weekly outdoor time was found to explain a significant amount of variance in wellbeing scores over and above weekly social interactions $(F(1 ,197) = 15.48, p<.001)$.

:::



